N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 7842.10 - Public notice

State Regulations
A notice containing the title, business address and
business telephone number of the records access officer and appeals person, and
the location where records can be seen or copied, and the business address of
the Committee on Open Government shall be posted on the State Energy Plan
website. Notes
